{"tid":1960780,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"CLS呀姐要我一退燒就反工","createTime":"2020-04-06T11:05:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T12:57:36.000Z","uid":350944,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5d4067d6898880e30f00cbfa2616809b487f70b6","tid":1960780,"uid":350944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:05:52.000Z","msg":"話說我早排發燒，呀姐要我一退燒，第二日就反工<br />\n雖然跟左佢一段日子，知道佢係工作狂。我都好緊張自己條數，都不該係咁危險時間要我同其他同事冒險囉<br />\n<br />\n我另一半仲要係航空業，搞到我d同事果2日都怕咗我，同我保持距離,嘢都唔同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想休息多2日都唔敢，更加唔敢同office 投訴，呢d時間比佢炒咗我都唔知點搵第二份工<br />\n佢令到個個同事都唔敢call sick<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：NTP loreal 旗下牌子"},{"pid":"dfb9e29157a7815c085b1b229c1c06f5e7dea7e2","tid":1960780,"uid":34419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:06:40.000Z","msg":"係咁入佢房咳"},{"pid":"88f527aa1e92e6294d1d5a3fdb791ca48dba71a4","tid":1960780,"uid":321977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:06:50.000Z","msg":"返囉，有咩事攬炒之嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79b9db8d2bd95e35f6a2f48add5a71269fb7113","tid":1960780,"uid":257974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:06:58.000Z","msg":"無醫生紙?"},{"pid":"b7b1ee259a8cb5fcb06ed13362033d3d97a0859a","tid":1960780,"uid":350944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfb9e29157a7815c085b1b229c1c06f5e7dea7e2","tid":1960780,"uid":34419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:06:40.000Z","msg":"係咁入佢房咳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:10:42.000Z","msg":"我只係一個小小售貨員<br />\n公司分A,B 組，我唔會同佢同一日反工"},{"pid":"fca8638f1e0f8a3b4f082a8f77e40d20c1a49a05","tid":1960780,"uid":350944,"like":0,"disl